POE::Component::Server::SimpleContent
=====================================

A companion component to POE::Component::Server::SimpleHTTP

But should be usable with other POE HTTP server components.

INSTALLATION
------------

The easiest way to install is via CPAN.

To install manually, unpack the sources.

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

ActiveState perl. Obtain 'nmake' from the following link:

<http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb;en-us;Q132084>

You may also want to investigate getting the Microsoft Visual C++ Toolkit 2003
<http://msdn.microsoft.com/visualc/vctoolkit2003/>
